      context: ['A Microsoft account can be linked to Outlook, OneDrive, Windows, Microsoft 365, purchase history and recovery keys. If someone gets in, they may read email, reset other accounts or access synced files.', 'Microsoft provides panels for security, recent activity, sign-in methods and devices. Reviewing them periodically is better than acting only after an alert.'],
